OL,3,CDrivers could be charged #20 a week to
OL,4,Cpark at city centre offices
OL,6,FPeople could be charged #20 a week to
OL,7,Fpark at their offices in Bristol city
OL,8,Fcentre.
OL,10,FThe workplace levy would aim to cut
OL,11,Fcongestion and air pollution while
OL,12,Fraising #10million a year to improve
OL,13,Fpublic transport options in the city.
OL,15,FBristol City Council says the levy
OL,16,Fwould affect roughly 9,000 people who
OL,17,Fcurrently park at their workplace for
OL,18,Ffree.
