OL,3,CDrivers could be charged #20 a week to
OL,4,Cpark at city centre offices
OL,6,FRather than charge the individual, the
OL,7,Fcouncil would bill every business
OL,8,Fwhich currently offers free parking
OL,9,Ffor staff. It would then be up to the
OL,10,Fbusiness as to whether they pass that
OL,11,Fcharge onto employees or not.
OL,13,FExceptions may be made for disabled
OL,14,Fpeople who rely on private cars,
OL,15,Fhospital workers and other groups.
OL,17,FBut the levy will not be introduced
OL,18,Fquickly. It is expected to take about
OL,19,Fthree years to bring in, with
OL,20,Fcouncillors set to approve the levy at
OL,21,Fa meeting on 12 September.
