OL,6,F"The introduction of a levy has other
OL,7,Fbenefits associated with the reduction
OL,8,Fin car use and increase in alternative
OL,9,Fmodes such as walking, cycling and
OL,10,Fpublic transport, such as improvements
OL,11,Fto health and the environment.
OL,12,FEssentially, workplaces with parking
OL,13,Fplaces would face an annual charge per
OL,14,Fparking place and the employer would
OL,15,Fdecide whether to pass that compulsory
OL,16,Fcharge onto the employee or not."
