OL,3,CDrivers could be charged #20 a week to
OL,4,Cpark at city centre offices
OL,6,FA workplace parking levy was included
OL,7,Fin the Green Party's manifesto ahead
OL,8,Fof the local elections in May this
OL,9,Fyear. A similar charge was rolled out
OL,10,Fin Nottingham in 2012, which has since
OL,11,Fraised #83million to be spent on
OL,12,Fupgrading public transport such as the
OL,13,Fcity's tram network.
OL,15,FAccording to the report, multi-storey
OL,16,Fcar parks owned by the council have
OL,17,Fannual season tickets costing between
OL,18,F#54 and #72 a week. The cost of an
OL,19,Fannual First Bus Bristol Zone pass is
OL,20,F#841, or #16 per week.
